10.1 Inject Device Detection Framework

Build a cross-platform device detection layer in Node/Rust/Python.
Detect USB devices, serial numbers, chipsets, drivers, and OS capabilities.

10.2 Build BootForge USB Driver Layer

Create a safe, cross-platform Rust USB driver subsystem with modular adapters.
Include device scanning, DFU detection, logging, and error codes.

10.3 Build Trapdoor Tool Registry

Generate the architecture for a private CLI registry that loads binaries, runs payloads, logs results, and handles sandboxed subprocesses.
